The bash script is untested.
The install script is incomplete.
The powershell script might not work properly.
The python scripts dont work with python 2.7 installed apparently.
Good luck!

Install python 3 and pip
	https://www.python.org/ftp/python/3.5.2/python-3.5.2.exe
Install selenium
	http://selenium-python.readthedocs.io/installation.html
	pip install selenium
Install and setup the Firefox webdriver
	https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Mozilla/QA/Marionette/WebDriver
	https://github.com/mozilla/geckodriver/releases
	Extract the geckodriver executable to a location of your chosing
	Add that location to the System PATH
Enjoy
	